interesting points: The object was silent and remained stationary for the entire observation period,The object was described as slightly bluish white and bubble-like,The length of the sighting was approximately 30 minutes,The case was deemed inconclusive due to similarities with reflecting radar waves, yet there was no account for the reported visual sighting or duration,The object exhibited rapid upward motion at one point.
